<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.8">
<l>tōytta tayirum naṟuneyyum pālumō  rōrkkuṭaṉ tuṟṟi ṭumeṉ</l>
<l>ṟāycciyar kūṭi yaḻaikkavum nāṉitaṟ keḷki yivaṉai naṅkāy</l>
<l>cōttam pirāṉivai ceyyap peṟāyeṉ ṟirappa ṉurappa killēṉ</l>
<l>pēycci mulaiyuṇṭa piṉṉaiyip piḷḷaiyaip pēcuva tañcu vēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though the herder ladies shouted all together, “He gobbled up</l>
<l>Each and every pot of thick curds, fragrant ghee, and milk,”</l>
<l rend="indent">being embarrassed for this,</l>
<l>Ladies, I entreat him, “Greetings, lord. You do not get to do this”;</l>
<l rend="indent">but I cannot be firm.</l>
<l>After he ate from the demoness’ breasts,</l>
<l rend="indent">I am afraid of speaking up to this child.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
